data.description: Beautiful home situated convenient to all roads N,S, E,& W. The great neighborhood of Golden Meadows offers, safety, well built homes and a great sense of neighborhood. This home offers an open floor plan between Living, Dinning, kitchen & family rooms creating a never ending entertaining and life style flow. A new kitchen and appliances, updated bathrooms and 3 year old Central Air with the compliment of Hydro-air, enhances efficiency and year round comfort. The entire main floor is clad in new Laminate flooring and lots of windows flooding the home with light and opening up views. The bedrooms are all large because the home is wide in dimensions the bedrooms accommodate better living and bigger furniture. The lower level houses a game/play/office a large laundry room and crafting area also the oversized 2 car garage. Don't miss out on this beautiful home. 24 hours advanced notice please, Monday through Saturday 3:30 to 6, Sunday 10 to 5.. Thank you
